## Memory Budgets

### Per-Process Limits (Approximate)

| Platform | Typical Limit | Low-End Devices |
|----------|---------------|-----------------|
| iOS | 1-2 GB | 512 MB |
| Android | 256-512 MB (varies) | 128 MB |

### Budget Guidelines

| Resource | Budget | Action when exceeded |
|----------|--------|---------------------|
| App heap | 150 MB (baseline) | Profile and reduce |
| Image cache | 50 MB | LRU eviction |
| Offline data | 100 MB | User-configurable; warn |
| Total memory | 200 MB (target) | Investigate leaks |

### Memory Checklist

- [ ] No retain cycles (use weak references for delegates/closures)
- [ ] Large objects released when not needed (images, caches)
- [ ] Memory warnings handled (iOS: didReceiveMemoryWarning; Android: onTrimMemory)
- [ ] Leak detection run in CI or pre-release (Xcode Leaks, LeakCanary)
- [ ] Profile on device, not just simulator

### Leak Detection

```kotlin
// Android: LeakCanary
dependencies {
  debugImplementation 'com.squareup.leakcanary:leakcanary-android:2.12'
}
```

```swift
// iOS: Enable Malloc Stack Logging in scheme
// Run with Instruments Leaks template
```

