## Battery Consumption

### Targets

| Scenario | Target | Measurement |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| Idle (background) | < 1% per hour | Xcode Energy Log, Android Battery Historian |
| Active use (1 hr) | < 15% drain | Same |
| Background fetch | Minimal; batch work | Limit frequency |

### Optimization Checklist

- [ ] Reduce wake locks; release as soon as work done
- [ ] Batch network requests; avoid frequent polling
- [ ] Use background task APIs correctly (iOS BGAppRefresh, Android WorkManager)
- [ ] Avoid unnecessary location updates (use significant change when possible)
- [ ] Profile with Energy Log (iOS) and Battery Historian (Android)
- [ ] Disable debug logging and analytics verbosity in release

### Network Efficiency

- [ ] Compress requests (gzip, Brotli)
- [ ] Use delta sync instead of full fetch when possible
- [ ] Cache responses; respect cache headers
- [ ] Prefer HTTP/2 or HTTP/3 for multiplexing
- [ ] Avoid large payloads; paginate lists
- [ ] Use CDN for static assets

---

## Network Efficiency

### Request Budgets

| Request Type | Target Latency | Max Payload |
|--------------|----------------|-------------|
| API call | < 500ms | 100 KB |
| List fetch | < 1s | 200 KB (paginated) |
| Image load | < 2s | Per-image budget |
| Initial data | < 2s | 500 KB total |

### Best Practices

- [ ] Request only needed fields (GraphQL, sparse fieldsets)
- [ ] Use pagination (limit 20-50 per page)
- [ ] Implement request deduplication
- [ ] Cancel in-flight requests when view dismissed
- [ ] Use connection pooling; reuse connections

---

## Profiling Workflow

### Pre-Release Checklist

- [ ] Cold start measured on minimum supported OS version
- [ ] Scroll performance tested with 100+ items
- [ ] Memory profiled for 10+ minutes of typical use
- [ ] No leaks detected
- [ ] Battery impact estimated (or measured) for key flows
- [ ] Profile on low-end device (e.g., older iPhone, budget Android)

### CI Integration

- [ ] Startup time regression test (fail if > 20% increase)
- [ ] Bundle size budget (fail if exceeded)
- [ ] Static analysis for obvious performance anti-patterns
- [ ] Manual profiling required for major releases

---

## Checklist Summary

| Area | Target |
|------|--------|
| Cold start | < 2.5s |
| Frame rate | 60 fps (120 on ProMotion) |
| Memory | < 200 MB baseline |
| Battery | < 1%/hr idle |
| Network | < 500ms API, paginated lists |
| Profiling | Before every release |
